{"data":[{"name":"56:1","price":"1. Quand adviendra l’Événement,","arabic":"إِذَا وَقَعَتِ ٱلۡوَاقِعَةُ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4980,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:2","price":"2. nul ne pourra en repousser la survenue.","arabic":"لَيۡسَ لِوَقۡعَتِهَا كَاذِبَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4981,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:3","price":"3. Il ravalera (les uns) et élèvera (les autres).","arabic":"خَافِضَةٞ رَّافِعَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4982,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:4","price":"4. Quand la terre sera ébranlée d’un fort ébranlement,","arabic":"إِذَا رُجَّتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ رَجّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4983,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:5","price":"5. que les montagnes seront entièrement pulvérisées,","arabic":"وَبُسَّتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ بَسّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4984,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:6","price":"6. et seront alors poussière dispersée, ","arabic":"فَكَانَتۡ هَبَآءٗ مُّنۢبَثّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4985,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:7","price":"7. vous (vous diviserez) alors en trois groupes.","arabic":"وَكُنتُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا ثَلَٰثَةٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4986,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:8","price":"8. (D’abord), les gens de la dextre : mais que sont les gens de la dextre ?","arabic":"فَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4987,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:9","price":"9. (Puis) les gens de la senestre : mais que sont les gens de la senestre ?[543] ","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4988,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[543] Nous avons préféré employer les doublets savants et vieux : « dextre » et « senestre », au lieu de « droite » et « gauche » qui ont aujourd’hui des connotations renvoyant aux partis politiques.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:10","price":"10. (Enfin) les précurseurs (vers la foi et l’accomplissement des œuvres pies ici-bas), seront les précurseurs (vers les récompenses de l’au-delà) !","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ ٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4989,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:11","price":"11. Ceux-là seront les plus rapprochés (d’Allah),","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4990,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:12","price":"12. dans les Jardins des délices.","arabic":"فِي جَنَّٰتِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4991,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:13","price":"13. Nombre seront (choisis) parmi les générations premières,","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4992,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:14","price":"14. et peu seront (choisis) parmi les générations qui ont suivi.","arabic":"وَقَلِيلٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4993,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:15","price":"15. (Ils se reposeront) sur des lits incrustés d’or,","arabic":"عَلَىٰ سُرُرٖ مَّوۡضُونَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4994,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:16","price":"16. et seront accoudés face à face.","arabic":"مُّتَّكِـِٔينَ عَلَيۡهَا مُتَقَٰبِلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4995,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:17","price":"17. Parmi eux circuleront des jeunes serviteurs faits éternels,","arabic":"يَطُوفُ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وِلۡدَٰنٞ مُّخَلَّدُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4996,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:18","price":"18. (portant) des coupes, des brocs et un verre rempli (d’un vin) coulant d’une source intarissable,","arabic":"بِأَكۡوَابٖ وَأَبَارِيقَ وَكَأۡسٖ مِّن مَّعِينٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4997,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:19","price":"19. qui ne leur donnera pas (le moindre) mal de tête ni ne les fera divaguer .","arabic":"لَّا يُصَدَّعُونَ عَنۡهَا وَلَا يُنزِفُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4998,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:20","price":"20. Et (il y aura aussi) des fruits à leur goût,","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ مِّمَّا يَتَخَيَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4999,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:21","price":"21. la chair de volaille dont ils auront envie ;","arabic":"وَلَحۡمِ طَيۡرٖ مِّمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5000,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:22","price":"22. et des houris aux grands yeux noirs,","arabic":"وَحُورٌ عِينٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5001,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:23","price":"23. telles des perles soigneusement conservées (dans leur coquillage).","arabic":"كَأَمۡثَٰلِ ٱللُّؤۡلُوِٕ ٱلۡمَكۡنُونِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5002,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:24","price":"24. Voilà la récompense de leurs œuvres (ici-bas).","arabic":"جَزَآءَۢ بِمَا كَانُواْ يَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5003,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:25","price":"25. Ils n’y entendront ni discours futiles ni propos injurieux,","arabic":"لَا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا تَأۡثِيمًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5004,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:26","price":"26. mais seulement : « Paix ! Paix ! (Salâm ! Salâm !) »","arabic":"إِلَّا قِيلٗا سَلَٰمٗا سَلَٰمٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5005,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:27","price":"27. Les gens de la dextre : mais que sont les gens de la dextre ?","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5006,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:28","price":"28. (Ceux-là seront) parmi des lotus sans épines,","arabic":"فِي سِدۡرٖ مَّخۡضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5007,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:29","price":"29. et des fleurs d’acacias bellement disposées,","arabic":"وَطَلۡحٖ مَّنضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5008,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:30","price":"30. sous des ombres qui s’étendent,","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مَّمۡدُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5009,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:31","price":"31. auprès d’une eau coulant sans cesse,","arabic":"وَمَآءٖ مَّسۡكُوبٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5010,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:32","price":"32. et des fruits à profusion,","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ كَثِيرَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5011,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:33","price":"33. ni introuvables ni défendus. ","arabic":"لَّا مَقۡطُوعَةٖ وَلَا مَمۡنُوعَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5012,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:34","price":"34. Et (il y aura pour eux) des lits élevés.","arabic":"وَفُرُشٖ مَّرۡفُوعَةٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5013,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:35","price":"35. Nous les[544] avons  (véritablement) créées d’une création (nouvelle),","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنشَأۡنَٰهُنَّ إِنشَآءٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5014,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[544] Les houris du Paradis.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:36","price":"36. et nous en avons fait des vierges (éternelles),","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُنَّ أَبۡكَارًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5015,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:37","price":"37. pleines de tendresse et toutes du même âge,","arabic":"عُرُبًا أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5016,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:38","price":"38. à l’intention des gens de la dextre.","arabic":"لِّأَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5017,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:39","price":"39. Nombre seront (choisis) parmi les générations premières,","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5018,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:40","price":"40. et nombre seront (choisis) parmi les générations qui ont suivi.","arabic":"وَثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5019,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:41","price":"41. Quant aux gens de la senestre : mais que sont les gens de la senestre ?","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5020,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:42","price":"42. Ils seront au sein même du souffle infernal et (baigneront) dans l’eau bouillante,","arabic":"فِي سَمُومٖ وَحَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5021,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:43","price":"43. dans l’ombre d’une fumée épaisse et noire,","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مِّن يَحۡمُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5022,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:44","price":"44. ni fraîche ni clémente.","arabic":"لَّا بَارِدٖ وَلَا كَرِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5023,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:45","price":"45. Avant cela, ils étaient dans l’opulence,","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ قَبۡلَ ذَٰلِكَ مُتۡرَفِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5024,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:46","price":"46. et s’obstinaient dans le comble du péché.","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يُصِرُّونَ عَلَى ٱلۡحِنثِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5025,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:47","price":"47. Ils disaient : « Une fois que nous serons morts, réduits en poussière et ossements, serons-nous vraiment ressuscités ? ","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يَقُولُونَ أَئِذَا مِتۡنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابٗا وَعِظَٰمًا أَءِنَّا لَمَبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5026,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:48","price":"48. Et les premiers de nos ancêtres aussi ? »","arabic":"أَوَءَابَآؤُنَا ٱلۡأَوَّلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5027,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:49","price":"49. Dis : « Les premiers et les derniers ","arabic":"قُلۡ إِنَّ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ وَٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5028,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:50","price":"50. seront tous réunis pour le rendez-vous d’un jour déjà connu. »","arabic":"لَمَجۡمُوعُونَ إِلَىٰ مِيقَٰتِ يَوۡمٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5029,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:51","price":"51. Puis vous, les égarés, les négateurs,","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّكُمۡ أَيُّهَا ٱلضَّآلُّونَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5030,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:52","price":"52. vous mangerez certainement de l’arbre de Zaqqûm,","arabic":"لَأٓكِلُونَ مِن شَجَرٖ مِّن زَقُّومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5031,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:53","price":"53. et vos ventres en seront pleins.","arabic":"فَمَالِـُٔونَ مِنۡهَا ٱلۡبُطُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5032,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:54","price":"54. Puis vous ingurgiterez en plus une eau bouillante,","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ عَلَيۡهِ مِنَ ٱلۡحَمِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5033,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:55","price":"55. dont vous boirez goulûment ainsi que des chameaux qui meurent de soif. ","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ شُرۡبَ ٱلۡهِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5034,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:56","price":"56. Tel sera le repas d’arrivée au Jour de la Rétribution.","arabic":"هَٰذَا نُزُلُهُمۡ يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5035,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:57","price":"57. Nous vous avons créés, pourquoi ne croirez-vous donc pas (à votre résurrection)?","arabic":"نَحۡنُ خَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ فَلَوۡلَا تُصَدِّقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5036,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:58","price":"58. Avez-vous considéré ce que vous éjaculez ?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تُمۡنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5037,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:59","price":"59. Est-ce vous qui le créez ou est-ce Nous le Créateur ?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَخۡلُقُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡخَٰلِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5038,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:60","price":"60. C’est Nous Qui avons décrété la mort parmi vous, et personne ne Nous précédera ","arabic":"نَحۡنُ قَدَّرۡنَا بَيۡنَكُمُ ٱلۡمَوۡتَ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5039,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:61","price":"61. pour vous remplacer par d’autres comme vous, ni pour vous recréer en ce que vous ne sauriez connaître.","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ أَمۡثَٰلَكُمۡ وَنُنشِئَكُمۡ فِي مَا لَا تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5040,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:62","price":"62. Vous avez pourtant connu la première création, que n’y réfléchissez-vous pas ? ","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ عَلِمۡتُمُ ٱلنَّشۡأَةَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ فَلَوۡلَا تَذَكَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5041,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:63","price":"63. Ne voyez-vous pas ce que vous labourez ?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تَحۡرُثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5042,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:64","price":"64. Est-ce vous qui en semez (les graines), ou est-ce Nous le Semeur ?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَزۡرَعُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلزَّٰرِعُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5043,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:65","price":"65. Si Nous voulions, Nous en ferions un amas de débris, et vous n’en croiriez pas vos yeux.","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ لَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ حُطَٰمٗا فَظَلۡتُمۡ تَفَكَّهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5044,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:66","price":"66. « Nous voilà criblés de dettes !","arabic":"إِنَّا لَمُغۡرَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5045,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:67","price":"67. Ou nous voilà plutôt ruinés ! »","arabic":"بَلۡ نَحۡنُ مَحۡرُومُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5046,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:68","price":"68. Ne voyez-vous pas l’eau dont vous buvez ?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَآءَ ٱلَّذِي تَشۡرَبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5047,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:69","price":"69. Est-ce vous qui la faites descendre des nuages ou est-ce Nous qui le faisons ?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنزَلۡتُمُوهُ مِنَ ٱلۡمُزۡنِ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنزِلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5048,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:70","price":"70. Si Nous voulions, Nous en ferions une eau saumâtre. Que n’êtes-vous donc reconnaissants ?","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ جَعَلۡنَٰهُ أُجَاجٗا فَلَوۡلَا تَشۡكُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5049,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:71","price":"71. Ne voyez-vous pas le feu que vous allumez ?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلنَّارَ ٱلَّتِي تُورُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5050,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:72","price":"72. Est-ce vous qui avez créé l’arbre (qui permet de l’allumer) ou est-ce Nous le Créateur ?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنشَأۡتُمۡ شَجَرَتَهَآ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنشِـُٔونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5051,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:73","price":"73. Nous avons fait (du feu) un rappel et un élément au service des hommes.[545]","arabic":"نَحۡنُ جَعَلۡنَٰهَا تَذۡكِرَةٗ وَمَتَٰعٗا لِّلۡمُقۡوِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5052,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[545] Littéralement : aux voyageurs qui campent dans le désert.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:74","price":"74. Rends donc gloire au nom de ton Seigneur, le Très Grand !","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5053,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:75","price":"75. Non ! J’en Jure par les positions des étoiles,","arabic":"۞ فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِمَوَٰقِعِ ٱلنُّجُومِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5054,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:76","price":"76. Et voilà le plus solennel des serments, si vous saviez,","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَقَسَمٞ لَّوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عَظِيمٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5055,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:77","price":"77. que c’est certes un Coran noble,","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقُرۡءَانٞ كَرِيمٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5056,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:78","price":"78. en un Livre protégé,","arabic":"فِي كِتَٰبٖ مَّكۡنُونٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5057,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:79","price":"79. et que ne touchent que les purifiés. ","arabic":"لَّا يَمَسُّهُۥٓ إِلَّا ٱلۡمُطَهَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5058,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:80","price":"80. C’est là une révélation du Seigneur de l’Univers.","arabic":"تَنزِيلٞ مِّن رَّبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5059,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:81","price":"81. Est-ce donc à ce discours-là[546] que vous refusez de croire ?","arabic":"أَفَبِهَٰذَا ٱلۡحَدِيثِ أَنتُم مُّدۡهِنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5060,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[546] Le Coran.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:82","price":"82. Serait-ce là votre manière de reconnaître les bienfaits que de tenir (le Coran) pour un mensonge ?","arabic":"وَتَجۡعَلُونَ رِزۡقَكُمۡ أَنَّكُمۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5061,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:83","price":"83. Lorsque ( avant d’être rendue) l’âme remonte jusqu’à la gorge,","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلۡحُلۡقُومَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5062,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:84","price":"84. alors que vous êtes là à regarder,","arabic":"وَأَنتُمۡ حِينَئِذٖ تَنظُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5063,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:85","price":"85. et que Nous sommes plus proches (du mourant) que vous ne l’êtes, mais vous ne le voyez pas,","arabic":"وَنَحۡنُ أَقۡرَبُ إِلَيۡهِ مِنكُمۡ وَلَٰكِن لَّا تُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5064,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:86","price":"86. pourquoi donc, si vous n’avez pas vraiment à payer pour vos œuvres, ","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ غَيۡرَ مَدِينِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5065,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:87","price":"87. ne la faites-vous pas revenir, si vous êtes sincères (dans vos dires) ?","arabic":"تَرۡجِعُونَهَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ صَٰدِقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5066,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:88","price":"88. Si (le défunt) est du nombre des privilégiés,[547]","arabic":"فَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5067,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"[547] Littéralement : des rapprochés.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:89","price":"89. Il y aura alors pour lui repos, grâce et Jardin des délices.","arabic":"فَرَوۡحٞ وَرَيۡحَانٞ وَجَنَّتُ نَعِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5068,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:90","price":"90. Et s’il est du nombre des gens de la dextre,","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5069,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:91","price":"91. Alors, « Paix à toi (lui sera-t-il dit), (ô toi qui fais partie) des gens de la dextre. »","arabic":"فَسَلَٰمٞ لَّكَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5070,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:92","price":"92. Et s’il est du nombre des négateurs fourvoyés,","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5071,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:93","price":"93. il sera l’hôte (de l’Enfer) où il sera abreuvé d’eau bouillante,","arabic":"فَنُزُلٞ مِّنۡ حَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5072,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:94","price":"94. et où il brûlera dans la Fournaise.","arabic":"وَتَصۡلِيَةُ جَحِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5073,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:95","price":"95. Telle est la véritable certitude.","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَهُوَ حَقُّ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5074,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"56:96","price":"96. Rends donc gloire au Nom de ton Seigneur, le Très Grand.","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5075,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah","Chapter Al-Waqi'ah","Waqi'ah","Surah Waqi'ah","Chapter Waqi'ah","Al Waqi'ah","Surah Al Waqi'ah","Chapter Al Waqi'ah","Surah 56","Chapter 56","The Inevitable","الواقعة"]}